{"tid":2436751,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"前法國大使駐英批強生愛說謊 擔心英脫歐恐面臨挑戰","createTime":"2021-03-07T11:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T11:57:43.000Z","uid":229777,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2049537b0052dc2ddef9db90e5be863d1a1dd783","tid":2436751,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:17:42.000Z","msg":"（法新社巴黎6日電） 前法國駐英國大使白林接受媒體訪問時表示，英國在首相強生帶領下脫離歐洲聯盟（EU）後，要保住全球影響力面臨艱難挑戰。她還說強生有個眾所周知的名聲，就是「愛說謊」。<br />\n<br />\n白林（Sylvie Bermann）2014至2017年出使倫敦，並對2016年的英國脫歐公投有第一手觀察。她今年1月出版法文新書「不列顛尼亞再見」（GoodbyeBritannia，暫譯），書中對這段經驗有些明顯不婉轉的評論，在英國引起一些人側目。<br />\n<br />\n白林在書中也毫不隱藏她對英國政壇深感失望，尤其是對那些帶領英國脫離歐盟的政治人物。她還將強生（Boris Johnson）形容為「毫無悔意的騙子」。<br />\n<br />\n曾任法國駐俄羅斯和駐中國大使的白林，在巴黎接受法新社訪問時表示：「究竟為什麽，當你（英國）在歐盟非常有活力、很成功且深具影響力時，為何會決定要離開？那樣會更辛苦，而且要花很多努力才能在世界上有真正影響力。」<br />\n<br />\n白林還指出，在美國和中國打「新冷戰」的地緣政治背景下，英國的處境將格外艱難，因為美中兩國都會看重歐盟而非英國。「這是一個三角關系，英國要（在其中）扮演角色會更困難。」<br />\n<br />\n白林並認為，英國大肆宣傳和美國間有「特殊關系」，但「最重要是對英國來說特殊」，而非對於美國。她說：「美國往往利用英國作為和歐盟間的橋梁或中介。顯然這個角色現在消失了。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%89%8D%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%A9%BB%E8%8B%B1%E6%89%B9%E5%BC%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%88%B1%E8%AF%B4%E8%B0%8E-%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%84%B1%E6%AC%A7%E6%81%90%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%B4%E6%8C%91%E6%88%98\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Fcn%2F%25E5%2589%258D%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259B%25BD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E9%25A9%25BB%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%25BC%25BA%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2588%25B1%25E8%25AF%25B4%25E8%25B0%258E-%25E6%258B%2585%25E5%25BF%2583%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%2584%25B1%25E6%25AC%25A7%25E6%2581%2590%25E9%259D%25A2%25E4%25B8%25B4%25E6%258C%2591%25E6%2588%2598&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=afec4b22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E5%89%8D%E6%B3%95%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E4%BD%BF%E9%A9%BB%E8%8B%B1%E6%89%B9%E5%BC%BA%E7%94%9F%E7%88%B1%E8%AF%B4%E8%B0%8E-%E6%8B%85%E5%BF%83%E8%8B%B1%E8%84%B1%E6%AC%A7%E6%81%90%E9%9D%A2%E4%B8%B4%E6%8C%91%E6%88%98</a>"},{"pid":"dd3cdd0eeb00072a3b2f3df0a006859d933d461d","tid":2436751,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3e8f324b43c0e5aae888871486fee3391fc315","tid":2436751,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:47:44.000Z","msg":"法國高稅, 法國企業衝晒去英國<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kWt0WjlGX_I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkWt0WjlGX_I&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=f72728be\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kWt0WjlGX_I</a>"},{"pid":"44108ef08a0e1ae3099853f750b08a626b0efb8c","tid":2436751,"uid":45518,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:53:29.000Z","msg":"公投結果，又關BJ事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d89d4bda15f25f8b2dacac775f96d380e0fc986a","tid":2436751,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:56:21.000Z","msg":"前一二戰極速秒敗的法國，其大使稱強生愛說謊 擔心英脫歐恐面臨挑戰  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得標題咁寫會中立d"},{"pid":"c4576eb0900f397e4a96bf9d282200515b2637a0","tid":2436751,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:57:02.000Z","msg":"脫左歐關你法國佬乜野事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擔心英國不如擔心下歐盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324cc831e943d9b06bb7628c85ca2989fa70b262","tid":2436751,"uid":35783,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T11:57:31.000Z","msg":"搞政治唔講大話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618